PeepShow
============

A sneaky preview for dirty objects.
View unsaved content in your show view.


Example
=======

  # Controller
  def show
    @post = peep_show(:post)
  end

  # Form View
  <%= submit_to_dirty_preview('Preview', @post) %>

  # Show View or Layout (optional)
  <%= peep_show_flash %>

